{"tid":1374074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰略分析]狗仔兵力偵察","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:16:05.000Z","uid":164008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"782917637ba035f3f88f1eff44efb42cb76086e1","tid":1374074,"uid":164008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:09:03.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今晚見各位為香港入元朗十分感動<br />\n而大家喺陳伯 議員 記 消防醫護等合力下全部離開<br />\n多謝各位嘅努力<br />\n<br />\n而賽後想同各位討論小弟今日嘅所見<br />\n<br />\n小弟今日11點就到咗元朗<br />\n主要睇到由狗屋 到YOHO 南邊圍 水車館街 到元朗公園<br />\n可以查出朝早狗方已有運兵路線同重兵之地<br />\n<br />\n如圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dOufQCJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdOufQCJ.jpg&h=572e567a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QerFhhK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQerFhhK.jpg&h=5b96823a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n可以見到 元朗公園開始全面調兵<br />\n3分鐘後大馬路出封鎖線<br />\n由於元朗地型獨特 只有東西兩個主要出口<br />\n地方唔大 若有事先偵察 大概可了解兵況<br />\n<br />\n於是問題:<br />\n喺日後各地活動 有無需要更多偵察行動 而非3點起點 先慢慢集合?<br />\n偵察情報 點樣快速傳到前線 讓前線若守若留 有早預算<br />\n<br />\n各位今日辛苦 戰事未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a534a725d9862d72e4f4ead490d43659ce5a733c","tid":1374074,"uid":164008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"自推 歡迎討論<br />\n提升戰略"},{"pid":"122452d3f1b8efdbbe333b4bd26f15aca4da9331","tid":1374074,"uid":164008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:12:00.000Z","msg":"自推 歡迎討論<br />\n提升戰略"},{"pid":"3521eb266ae2d042e90fe2af77806e3e45d441af","tid":1374074,"uid":164008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:16:05.000Z","msg":"自推 歡迎討論<br />\n提升戰略"}]}